31:24.592 --> 31:26.386
is that they have
the kind of women

31:26.553 --> 31:28.346
that I loved
when I was younger.

31:28.513 --> 31:30.807
Pale-skinned, blue-eyed.

31:30.974 --> 31:33.101
Hair so fair
it's almost white.

31:33.268 --> 31:34.686
Wine-coloured lips,

31:34.852 --> 31:36.354
full round breasts

31:36.521 --> 31:39.607
with veins running through them
like a good cheese.

31:40.650 --> 31:43.736
Only when you were younger?
You did alright last night.

31:44.862 --> 31:47.865
You want to know the secret
of my success?

31:48.032 --> 31:49.826
The secret is charm.

31:49.993 --> 31:52.620
Yeah, well,
you either got it or you don't.

31:52.787 --> 31:55.248
Charms can be learned
like anything else.

32:00.378 --> 32:02.505
♪ Saw a room full of men

32:02.672 --> 32:04.841
♪ With their hammers
a-bleedin'

32:05.008 --> 32:06.968
♪ And it's a hard

32:07.135 --> 32:09.178
♪ It's a hard

32:09.345 --> 32:12.932
♪ It's a hard
